## Expansion Path After MVP

When Phase 1 work begins, these are the expected structural changes and where they land:

| Phase 1 addition | Where it goes |
|---|---|
| User accounts | New `src/pages/account/` route; Zustand slice added to `src/stores/` |
| Stats API goes live | `useProfileStats` already exists ŌĆö no structural change |
| Additional shared components | `src/shared/` grows; no restructuring needed |
| `src/types.ts` grows past ~150 lines | Split into `src/types/domain.ts`, `src/types/manifest.ts` ŌĆö mechanical refactor |
| Second shared hook | `src/hooks/` already exists ŌĆö add alongside `useProfileStats` |
| Slicer override UI | Add `SlicerOverride.tsx` to `src/pages/configure/` |

No structural change is needed for Phase 1 unless user accounts are introduced. The current structure supports it without pre-emptive abstraction.
